{"id":161890,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/06/明報-公安部公布食品添加案例2246/","date":"2011-06-16T23:30:42Z","modified":"2011-06-17T05:48:05Z","title":"明報 | 公安部公布食品添加案例","content":"<p>中國公安部稱，今年以來，各地公安機關嚴厲打擊各種食品非法添加活動，破獲食品非法添加案件超過千一宗。</p>\n<div>\n<p>在行動中拘捕二千多人，為更加有力地震懾食品非法添加違法犯罪活動，當局公布了這類案件的十大典型案例：</p>\n<p>遼寧瀋陽蹇某等製售有毒、有害豆芽案；</p>\n<p>山東茌平雷某製售偽劣腐竹案；</p>\n<p>廣東羅某等製售偽劣食品案；</p>\n<p>重慶徐某等非法利用潲水油製售食用油案；</p>\n<p>江蘇江陰胡某等製售假牛肉案；</p>\n<p>河北石家莊張某等生產、銷售有毒有害食品案；</p>\n<p>黑龍江齊齊哈爾市張某等製售有毒、有害食品案；</p>\n<p>江西鷹潭陳某等製售有毒豆製品案；</p>\n<p>廣東東莞昱延食品有限公司製售有毒、有害食品添加劑案；</p>\n<p>遼寧大連王某製售有毒辣椒麵案。</p>\n<p>(新華社)</p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&amp;ip=1&amp;img=1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" /><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&amp;ip=1&amp;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fmingpao.feedsportal.com%2Fc%2F33528%2Ff%2F585672%2Fs%2F15f05085%2Fl%2F0Linews0Bmingpao0N0Chtm0CINews0C20A110A6160Cca42246c0Bhtm%2Fstory01.htm&amp;title=%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E9%83%A8%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%83%E9%A3%9F%E5%93%81%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E6%A1%88%E4%BE%8B%5B22%3A46%5D\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<p>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</p>\n<form action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\" method=\"POST\"> 定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=738338\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a></p>\n</form>\n","author":1,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}